Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inherited will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The tide of the times... People's dreams...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These things cannot be stopped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as people seek the answer of freedom,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}these things will never cease to be!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:42.02,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,mirai dake shinjiteru dareka ga warattemo kamawanai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:47.52,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,hashitteru jounetsu ga anata o kiramekaseru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:53.53,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,mabushi sugi, demo mitsumete itai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:57.03,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,dokka "bigaku" kanjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:03.71,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,dare ni mo nitenai yume no senaka o
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.98,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,oikakete oikaketeku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:10.27,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,doramatikku te ni ireru made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:22.33,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,dare ni mo mienai yume no katachi o
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:25.39,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,tsukamaete tsukamaeteku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:31.40,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,watashi wa tsuite yuku kara atsui kimochi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.49,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,tsujitsuma awase betsu ni iranai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:37.84,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,arifureta nichijou yori mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:41.08,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,paradaisu mezashite hashire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:42.02,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I only believe in the future, I don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:47.52,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,that racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:53.53,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,it's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:57.03,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:03.71,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I follow, follow in the footsteps of a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.98,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:10.27,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:22.33,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:25.39,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,of a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:31.40,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go with you, so passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.49,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I don't really need everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:37.84,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:41.08,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.94,0:01:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming! \NShoot it, quickly! Shoot it!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.21,0:02:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.97,0:02:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.01,0:02:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:36.78,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(352,105)}Through the Sky They Soar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:36.78,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\fs55\pos(401.5,460)}The 1,000-Year \NLegend Lives Again!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.78,0:02:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.23,0:02:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to going to the dragons' nest?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.08,0:02:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Try hard to live!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.08,0:02:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.00,0:02:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.17,0:02:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn those guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.50,0:02:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.92,0:02:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He can't swim, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.85,0:03:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew, what a scare...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.69,0:03:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It suddenly came right for me...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.78,0:03:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore! \NThe Millennial Dragon is starting to sink!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.65,0:03:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fret! We'll still make it in time!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.20,0:03:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire a harpoon and drag it in!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.26,0:03:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Target the Millennial Dragon!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.76,0:03:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Fire!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.61,0:04:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.66,0:04:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You've no idea of the value of the \Nthing you're standing on right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.58,0:04:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want are the Millennial Dragon's bones!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.30,0:04:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I have its Dragonite, \NI can attain everlasting life!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.85,0:04:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.75,0:04:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu isn't a thing! \NHe's our friend!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.22,0:04:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a dear friend who's on a journey with us!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.88,0:05:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What utter nonsense!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.00,0:05:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, you can sink \Ninto the sea with your friend!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.26,0:05:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you try to harpoon me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.68,0:05:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire at that brat!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.97,0:05:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But, if we do that, we'll blow \Nthe Millennial Dragon up, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.52,0:05:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter! \NBone fragments will do just fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.23,0:05:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir! \NAim the sub-cannons out to sea!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.65,0:05:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.07,0:05:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fine staying here?! \NWhat kind of wimpiness is that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You still haven't accomplished your goal!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.71,0:05:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to going to your nest?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.62,0:05:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up by saying you're staying here!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.25,0:05:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I will! \NDon't worry about Apis!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.91,0:05:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just think about yourself now!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.98,0:05:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Untie these ropes!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.56,0:06:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,– I gotta go to Grandpa Ryu! \N– What's that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.32,0:06:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta save Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.52,0:06:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Leave Grandpa Ryu to Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.03,0:06:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no! \NI gotta go! I gotta go!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.03,0:06:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone, he'll manage somehow!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.33,0:06:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire sea is shaking!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.45,0:06:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?! What's happening?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.64,0:06:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.81,0:06:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?! What the...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.52,0:06:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.19,0:06:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}that's{\i0} it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.49,0:06:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What is happening?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.13,0:06:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There shouldn't be any underwater \Nvolcanoes in these waters!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.16,0:07:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter! Fire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.73,0:07:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.24,0:07:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You have dear friends of your own, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.50,0:07:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.72,0:07:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he bellowing for?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.00,0:07:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's calling...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.84,0:07:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.80,0:07:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's telling Millennial Dragons \Nall around the world that it's "time"...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.40,0:07:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "time"?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.47,0:08:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! W-What's that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.96,0:08:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So many Millennial Dragons!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.00,0:08:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,These're Grandpa Ryu's friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.34,0:08:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell'd they come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Those are...!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.14,0:08:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragonite! \NIt's a mother lode of Dragonite!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.44,0:08:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot them! Shoot them down!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.03,0:08:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We can't! \NOur cannons can't reach that high!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.37,0:09:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.92,0:09:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I know! \NI promise I'll tell Apis!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.95,0:09:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.17,0:09:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...Rocket!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.46,0:09:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Gonna borrow your neck!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.30,0:09:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...And...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...Battle-Axe!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.81,0:10:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.49,0:10:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.46,0:11:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.38,0:11:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The commodore's been beaten!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.60,0:11:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Troops sure are weak once \Ntheir bosses are taken out.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.16,0:11:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they just gonna reel in \Ntheir chains and run away?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We better get goin' too.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.95,0:11:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're circling around... \NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.08,0:11:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.94,0:11:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.41,0:11:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The chains!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.50,0:11:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiots! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.00,0:11:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna crash!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.26,0:12:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really somethin'!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.55,0:12:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}! I'm back!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.22,0:12:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get on already!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.85,0:12:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.81,0:12:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...Rocket!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.52,0:12:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you again!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.65,0:12:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.36,0:12:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me, "Yo!"
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.45,0:12:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you come back more quietly?! \NYou're gonna wreck the ship!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.41,0:12:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.46,0:12:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,An earthquake?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.38,0:12:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.79,0:12:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.63,0:12:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to keep my \Npromise to you, Grandpa Ryu...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.38,0:12:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to take you to the dragons' nest...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.18,0:12:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Grandpa Ryu's wish came true.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.06,0:13:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you hear the Millennial Dragons' voices?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.58,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.79,0:13:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with these earthquakes?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.21,0:13:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This one's big!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.55,0:13:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,T-The sea's pulling way back!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.61,0:13:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what it meant!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.28,0:13:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The dragons' nest really {\i1}is{\i0} here!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.87,0:13:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not called "Millennial Dragons" \Nbecause of their life spans!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.96,0:14:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because they come to this \Nisland only once every 1,000 years!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.01,0:14:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Millennial Dragons are migratory!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.39,0:14:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's by no coincidence that \Nthey've all flocked here now!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.89,0:14:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder they call it Lost Island!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.57,0:14:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it only surfaces \Nonce every 1,000 years!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.77,0:14:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So of course no one today \Nremembers the last time it surfaced!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.82,0:14:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And now... this very moment...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.07,0:14:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...is when the dragons' nest has appeared!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.23,0:15:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.76,0:15:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, is that what I think it is?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.02,0:15:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It must be the dragon nest \NGrandpa Ryu wanted to go back to!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.57,0:15:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This{\i0} is?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.07,0:15:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Apis!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.45,0:15:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Apis!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.41,0:16:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd she suddenly run off?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.29,0:16:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu is here...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.05,0:16:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.30,0:16:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.43,0:16:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.69,0:16:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just by coincidence, the place Grandpa Ryu sunk
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.69,0:16:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,was where the dragons' nest was...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.61,0:16:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you suppose that might \Nhelp him rest in peace better?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.69,0:16:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay! \NHe said his wish came true when he was sinking!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.25,0:16:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the dragons' nest? \NLook at all these weird rocks...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.71,0:16:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they're probably made of Dragonite...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.96,0:16:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.17,0:16:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this rock here. \NDoesn't it look just like a dragon?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.55,0:16:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But why are the rocks dragons?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.05,0:17:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they were on the ocean floor for a thousand long years.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.86,0:17:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The materials in their bodies fossilized.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.52,0:17:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.81,0:17:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you {\i1}really{\i0} get it?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.97,0:17:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope! Not at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.52,0:17:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They say when elephants are about to die,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.48,0:17:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,they hide themselves in their elephant graveyard.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.86,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the same is true here. \NThis might be a dragon graveyard...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.78,0:17:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A dragon graveyard?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.24,0:17:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's not!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.08,0:17:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu said going back \Nto his nest would make him better!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.17,0:17:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This {\i1}can't{\i0} be a graveyard!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.63,0:17:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Apis...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.92,0:17:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu was a lost Millennial Dragon...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.43,0:17:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.69,0:17:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He was all alone, for a thousand years...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.64,0:17:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But he made friends with you, Apis.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.69,0:17:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He said out of the 1,000 years he was alive,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.23,0:17:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,this last year with you was his happiest.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.91,0:18:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy... You understand the dragons' language?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.16,0:18:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I just somehow know.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.33,0:18:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, talk about half-baked...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.37,0:18:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.14,0:18:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You liar...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.84,0:18:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a liar, Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.83,0:18:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is the dragons' nest...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've made it back to the dragons' nest,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.92,0:18:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,then open your eyes again!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.88,0:18:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Get better!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.36,0:18:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu wasn't lying at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.15,0:18:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that Millennial Dragons \Nreturn to the nest every 1,000 years
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.29,0:18:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and are reborn again.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu said that?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.75,0:18:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A baby Millennial Dragon?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.09,0:19:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.11,0:19:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.99,0:20:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Apis.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.95,0:20:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't just a Millennial Dragon graveyard.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.58,0:20:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's a place that connects to new life.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.46,0:20:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.00,0:20:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.00,0:20:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,For bringing Grandpa Ryu \Nback to the dragons' nest.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.76,0:20:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize it now, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.55,0:20:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize what kind of place this is,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.80,0:20:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and why Grandpa Ryu \Nwanted to return here so badly.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.10,0:20:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Apis...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.55,0:20:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an amazing place, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.77,0:20:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I understand why my ancestors \Nwent so far as to build a temple...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.90,0:20:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's go back to the village!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.28,0:20:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone there must be worried, \Nand probably surprised, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.87,0:20:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.17,0:20:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.54,0:21:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry back to the ship and leave the island!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.80,0:21:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.09,0:21:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew, I'm starving!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.30,0:21:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji! Make me some food!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.30,0:21:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,– Yeah! \N– Meat! Make meat!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.02,0:21:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have sautéed veggies \Nwith lots of bean sprouts!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.56,0:21:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where've I heard that before?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.52,0:21:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, these rocks are cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.05,0:21:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,These all used to be Millennial Dragons?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.90,0:21:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it looks that way.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.40,0:21:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they {\i1}are{\i0} Dragonite, \Nthere's no way to extract it like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.24,0:21:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the whole elixir of immortality thing...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.74,0:21:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...was nothing but a dream within a dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.87,0:21:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we took these \Ncoral-covered fossils back with us,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.41,0:21:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd never get an elixir from them.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.21,0:21:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.92,0:21:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning those Navy bastards \Ndid all that work for nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.43,0:21:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools! \NAs if I would ever kick the bucket so easily!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.43,0:21:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}must{\i0} pay you back for what you've done!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.06,0:22:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But first...!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.44,0:22:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Millennial Dragons!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.82,0:22:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,With this many, I can have \Nall the Dragonite I want!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.74,0:22:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.29,0:22:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Eric! Look! \NA flock of Millennial Dragons!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.79,0:22:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay you money! \NWhat do you say to another deal?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.80,0:22:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We can make elixirs of immortality \Nfrom living Millennial Drag...!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.22,0:22:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way!
