Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:06.77,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.78,0:23:11.67,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:16.66,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}so keep watching me intently as I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.66,0:23:26.46,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}I was thinking about it a bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:31.46,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:37.64,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}starting from some point,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:41.47,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}I haven't been able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.77,0:23:47.79,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}I want to catch those feelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.79,0:23:52.62,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}and I'm already about to overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.62,0:23:57.37,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}I want to embrace my dreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.36,0:24:02.87,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}with you, I can run there
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.99,0:24:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Eric!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:12.07,0:24:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, he's stubborn!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:13.32,0:24:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll handle him.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.16,0:24:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I will!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:15.82,0:24:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:16.91,0:24:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Lost Island, huh? \NIt's sad to leave it now.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.33,0:24:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Set sail!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.33,0:24:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand Line, at last! \NIsn't this great?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:24.00,0:24:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can't wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.50,0:24:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.63,0:24:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the Red Line!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:28.55,0:24:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 10,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,An Angry Showdown! \NCross the Red Line!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:32.72,0:24:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
